flowchart TB
    subgraph prepare [准备阶段]
        A1[创建任务]
        A2[预检查]
        A1 --> A2
    end

    subgraph execute [执行阶段]
        B1["结构迁移<br/>DBCat"]
        B2["全量迁移<br/>FullImport"]
        B3["增量同步<br/>Store + IncrSync"]
        B1 --> B2 --> B3
    end

    subgraph finish [收尾阶段]
        C1["数据校验<br/>FullVerification"]
        C2[业务切换]
        C3[完成]
        C1 --> C2 --> C3
    end

    A2 -->|通过| B1
    A2 -.->|失败| Fail[终止或返回修改]
    B3 -->|延迟达标| C1
    C1 -.->|有差异| Repair[订正后复检]
    Repair --> C1
